  <brief_title>Feasibility Study Assessing the Treatment of Fibroadenomata With a Circumferential Sonication Treatment With HIFU</brief_title>
  <official_title>High Intensity Focused Ultrasound for the Treatment of Fibroadenomata (HIFU-F)</official_title>
